metadata.name: White Pepes Can't Jump
metadata.description:
Woody Pepelson is a basketball hustler who banks on players underestimating his skills on the court. When he pulls one over on Pepsley Snipes, his victim sees a lucrative opportunity, and they become partners in the con game, plying their trade across the courts of Los Angeles. 

Comes with the original framed artwork 15 inch x 12 inch.
